{
  "startEventId": "prologue_wake_up",
  "events": [
    {
      "id": "prologue_wake_up",
      "title": "雾莓镇的清晨",
      "presentation": "visualNovel",
      "backgroundId": "room_morning",
      "dialogue": [
        { "speakerId": "narrator", "speakerName": "旁白", "text": "晨光从斜斜的小窗照进来，落在梁上晾着的药草束上，把整间魔女小屋都晒出一点暖意。" },
        { "speakerId": "narrator", "speakerName": "旁白", "text": "木桌上摊着昨晚抄到一半的笔记，旧书压着几片卷边的叶子，杯底还留着草药茶微苦的香气。" },
        { "speakerId": "narrator", "speakerName": "旁白", "text": "透过窗子，雾莓镇还裹在轻雾里。石板路、低矮屋顶和远处的钟楼都像刚准备醒来。" },
        { "speakerId": "me", "speakerName": "我", "text": "今天就是第一天了。再紧张，也该像个真正的见习魔女那样出门。" },
        { "speakerId": "narrator", "speakerName": "旁白", "text": "门外传来瓷杯轻碰木盘的声音，有人显然比你更早开始了今天。" }
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "起身去看看",
          "effects": [{ "type": "setFlag", "key": "prologue_started", "value": true }],
          "next": { "eventId": "prologue_lilith_intro", "locationId": "home" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "prologue_lilith_intro",
      "title": "莉莉丝",
      "presentation": "visualNovel",
      "backgroundId": "room_morning",
      "characters": [
        {
          "id": "lilith",
          "name": "莉莉丝",
          "position": "right",
          "defaultSpriteId": "mentor_neutral",
          "defaultExpression": "平静"
        }
      ],
      "dialogue": [
        { "speakerId": "lilith", "speakerName": "莉莉丝", "spriteId": "mentor_neutral", "text": "终于醒了，亲爱的。我差点以为你打算把见习第一天也安排进梦里完成。" },
        { "speakerId": "narrator", "speakerName": "旁白", "text": "莉莉丝正靠在门边，手里端着一只浅口瓷杯。她看上去像刚散步回来，连晨雾都没舍得碰乱她的头发。" },
        { "speakerId": "me", "speakerName": "我", "text": "所以，从今天起就算正式开始了？" },
        { "speakerId": "lilith", "speakerName": "莉莉丝", "spriteId": "mentor_neutral", "text": "当然。真正的魔女生活不是坐在屋里把自己想得很了不起，而是走出去，认识小镇，接下委托，也让别人慢慢认识你。" },
        { "speakerId": "lilith", "speakerName": "莉莉丝", "spriteId": "mentor_neutral", "text": "你总得先学会和雾莓镇打招呼，它才会把日子一点点交给你。" }
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "听她安排今天",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "met_lilith", "value": true },
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "lilith_intro_seen", "value": true }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "prologue_first_choice", "locationId": "home" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "prologue_first_choice",
      "title": "今天想怎么开始",
      "presentation": "visualNovel",
      "backgroundId": "room_morning",
      "characters": [
        {
          "id": "lilith",
          "name": "莉莉丝",
          "position": "right",
          "defaultSpriteId": "mentor_neutral",
          "defaultExpression": "平静"
        }
      ],
      "dialogue": [
        { "speakerId": "lilith", "speakerName": "莉莉丝", "spriteId": "mentor_neutral", "text": "不过别急着摆出那种要和命运决斗的表情。第一天只需要一个还算像样的开头。" },
        { "speakerId": "lilith", "speakerName": "莉莉丝", "spriteId": "mentor_neutral", "text": "告诉我吧，今天的你，准备先当个认真的孩子、好奇的孩子，还是肚子饿的孩子？" }
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "我会努力成为合格的魔女",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "prologue_first_choice_done", "value": true }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "cottage_first_morning", "locationId": "home" }
        },
        {
          "text": "雾莓镇今天会发生什么",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "prologue_first_choice_done", "value": true }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "cottage_first_morning", "locationId": "home" }
        },
        {
          "text": "可以先吃早饭再开始吗",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "prologue_first_choice_done", "value": true }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "cottage_first_morning", "locationId": "home" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "cottage_first_morning",
      "title": "魔女小屋",
      "paragraphs": [
        "莉莉丝把杯子放到桌角，像是把今天也一并留给了你。魔女小屋不大，却什么都刚刚好：能读书，能配药，能发呆，也能在天黑以后带着一身风尘回来。",
        "从今往后，这里会是你的据点。你可以在这儿整理状态、看看手头的事，再决定要不要推门去见雾莓镇。",
        "门外的晨雾已经薄了些，石板路正一点点亮起来。第一天不会替你做决定，但它已经安静地等着你。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "整理一下桌面和笔记",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "addAttr", "key": "focus", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 20 }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "cottage_first_morning", "locationId": "home" }
        },
        {
          "text": "翻翻旧书上的边注",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "attr", "key": "intelligence", "op": "gte", "value": 1 }],
          "effects": [
            { "type": "addAttr", "key": "intelligence", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 20 }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "cottage_first_morning", "locationId": "home" }
        },
        {
          "text": "推门出去看看雾莓镇",
          "next": { "eventId": "fogberry_map_intro", "locationId": "home" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "fogberry_map_intro",
      "title": "雾莓镇",
      "paragraphs": [
        "门一打开，带着水气的清晨空气就贴上了你的脸。魔女小屋静静立在镇边，像一枚被雾藏起来的句号。",
        "沿着石板路往前，是最先热闹起来的市集和什么都能买到一点的杂货铺；再远些，有安静得像会把心事收好的圣殿、带着危险气味的魔物森林，还有白天懒洋洋、夜里才真正醒来的酒吧。",
        "你不需要今天就弄明白这座镇子的全部秘密。从现在开始，雾莓镇已经向你开放，你可以自由探索它。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "沿着石板路走进镇子",
          "effects": [{ "type": "setFlag", "key": "fogberry_map_intro_seen", "value": true }],
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "market_first_visit",
      "title": "市集",
      "paragraphs": [
        "白天的市集比魔女小屋热闹得多。摊位挨着摊位，水果香、香料味和讨价还价的声音把整条街都搅得很有精神。",
        "如果想知道一座小镇今天过得怎么样，先来市集总不会错。这里像雾莓镇最会说话的一张脸。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "慢慢看看摊位",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "addAttr", "key": "focus", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 20 }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "market_first_visit", "locationId": "market" }
        },
        {
          "text": "和摊主打听几句消息",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "addAttr", "key": "friendship", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 20 }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "market_first_visit", "locationId": "market" }
        },
        {
          "text": "顺着那道熟悉的笑声找过去",
          "conditions": [{ "type": "flag", "key": "lilith_first_meeting_done", "value": false }],
          "next": { "eventId": "lilith_first_meeting", "locationId": "market" }
        },
        {
          "text": "离开",
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "lilith_first_meeting",
      "title": "导师的闲逛",
      "presentation": "visualNovel",
      "backgroundId": "room_morning",
      "characters": [
        {
          "id": "lilith",
          "name": "莉莉丝",
          "position": "right",
          "defaultSpriteId": "mentor_neutral",
          "defaultExpression": "愉快"
        }
      ],
      "dialogue": [
        { "speakerId": "lilith", "speakerName": "莉莉丝", "spriteId": "mentor_neutral", "text": "你也来市集？不错，亲爱的，你终于学会用脚而不是用幻想生活了。" },
        { "speakerId": "me", "speakerName": "我", "text": "你为什么总能比我先一步出现在该出现的地方？" },
        { "speakerId": "lilith", "speakerName": "莉莉丝", "spriteId": "mentor_neutral", "text": "因为我比你更愿意按时出门。另一个原因，等你再长大一点我再告诉你。" }
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "问她今天该先做什么",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "lilith_first_meeting_done", "value": true },
            { "type": "addAttr", "key": "focus", "value": 1 }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "market_first_visit", "locationId": "market" }
        },
        {
          "text": "假装自己一点也不惊讶",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "setFlag", "key": "lilith_first_meeting_done", "value": true },
            { "type": "addAttr", "key": "charisma", "value": 1 }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "market_first_visit", "locationId": "market" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "grocery_first_visit",
      "title": "杂货铺",
      "paragraphs": [
        "不大的杂货铺里塞满了糖果、线团、空白本子、蜡烛和一些用途暧昧的小玩意儿，看上去总会让人顺手多拿一样。",
        "店里有种让人安心的生活气息。就算今天什么都不买，你也知道自己以后会常来。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "把环境记下来",
          "effects": [{ "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 10 }],
          "next": { "eventId": "grocery_first_visit", "locationId": "grocery" }
        },
        {
          "text": "离开",
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "church_first_visit",
      "title": "圣殿 / 教堂",
      "paragraphs": [
        "长椅、烛火和很轻的祷词把这里衬得安静又宽容，像一种不会追问你缘由的平静。",
        "你在门口停了停，忽然觉得连呼吸都该放轻一点。某些心事，也许以后可以拿到这里来想。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "安静地坐一会儿",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "addAttr", "key": "sanity", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 20 }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "church_first_visit", "locationId": "church" }
        },
        {
          "text": "离开",
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "forest_edge_first_visit",
      "title": "魔物森林",
      "paragraphs": [
        "林地边缘的潮气裹着泥土和草叶味，安静得有些过分，像是连脚下的影子都比镇上更深一点。",
        "这里当然不只是风景。你还没准备好立刻深入，但已经能感觉到，总有一天它会正式把你叫进去。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "在边缘观察一会儿",
          "effects": [
            { "type": "addAttr", "key": "proficiency", "value": 1 },
            { "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 20 }
          ],
          "next": { "eventId": "forest_edge_first_visit", "locationId": "forest" }
        },
        {
          "text": "先不进去",
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "bar_first_visit",
      "title": "酒吧",
      "paragraphs": [
        "白天的酒吧还没真正醒过来，门窗都带着一种懒洋洋的克制，像把夜里的喧闹和秘密先好好锁了起来。",
        "你把它的位置记在心里。等雾莓镇入夜以后，这里多半会是另一副模样。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "离开",
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "lilith_talk_church",
      "title": "莉莉丝",
      "paragraphs": [
        "莉莉丝坐在最后一排，手里拿着一本倒着翻的祷文。",
        "她抬眼看你，像是早就知道你会在这个时间出现。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "回到镇上",
          "effects": [{ "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 10 }],
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "lilith_talk_market",
      "title": "莉莉丝",
      "paragraphs": [
        "莉莉丝正站在摊位前，认真比较两瓶颜色可疑的小甜水。",
        "她朝你晃了晃手里的瓶子，笑得像是已经替你做完了选择。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "陪她聊一会儿",
          "effects": [{ "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 10 }],
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "lilith_talk_grocery",
      "title": "莉莉丝",
      "paragraphs": [
        "莉莉丝把一盒包装过度的糖果放回货架，又若无其事地重新拿起。",
        "她显然把这种无意义的比较当成了一种娱乐。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "听她点评糖果",
          "effects": [{ "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 10 }],
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "lilith_talk_bar",
      "title": "莉莉丝",
      "paragraphs": [
        "莉莉丝坐在吧台边，杯子里浮着一片发光的薄荷叶。",
        "她向你举杯，像夜色本身也欠她一句问候。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "在吧台边坐一会儿",
          "effects": [{ "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 10 }],
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "lilith_reality_chat",
      "title": "近况",
      "paragraphs": [
        "莉莉丝正了正头，像是从很远的地方听见了现实的回声。"
      ],
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "回到镇上",
          "effects": [{ "type": "advanceTime", "minutes": 10 }],
          "route": "map"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "map": [
    { "id": "home", "name": "魔女小屋", "neighbors": ["market", "grocery", "church"] },
